---
import PreviewLayout from '../../layouts/PreviewLayout.astro';
import ActionLinks from '../../components/ActionLinks.astro';
import HoursPanel from '../../components/HoursPanel.astro';
import AccessPanel from '../../components/AccessPanel.astro';
import PreviewPatternNav from '../../components/PreviewPatternNav.astro';
import { getAllProducts } from '../../data/products';
import productsImage from '../../assets/images/Products.jpg';
const products = getAllProducts().slice(0, 3);
const featureStyle = `--feature-image: url(${productsImage.src})`;
---
<PreviewLayout title="Pharmacy Magazine" theme="pharmacy-magazine" description="Codex再作成版。商品・健康コラム拡張を想定したマガジン型デザイン案です。">
  <article class="codex-pattern pattern-magazine"><section class="magazine-hero"><div class="preview-container"><PreviewPatternNav /><div class="magazine-grid"><main class="feature-article" style={featureStyle}><span class="codex-kicker">Codex redesign / Magazine</span><h1>季節の相談と、取扱い商品を読む。</h1><p>商品ページや健康コラムを増やしていく前提の編集面です。</p></main><aside class="magazine-side"><article><h2>Guide</h2><p>LINE受付の流れを読み物として案内。</p></article><article><h2>Shop Info</h2><HoursPanel /></article></aside></div></div></section><section class="preview-section"><div class="preview-container codex-product-list">{products.map((product) => <article class="codex-product-card"><span>{product.category}</span><h3>{product.name}</h3><p>{product.summary}</p></article>)}</div></section><section class="preview-section"><div class="preview-container care-info"><ActionLinks /><AccessPanel /></div></section></article>
</PreviewLayout>
